item.title: CVE-2022-4401|2024-10-15T17:12:56.238Z -- pallidlight -- online-course-selection-system
item.description: A vulnerability was found in pallidlight online-course-selection-system. It has been classified as problematic. Affected is an unknown function. The manipulation leads to cross site scripting. It is possible to launch the attack remotely. The identifier of this vulnerability is VDB-215268.
